item.description:
This is a closed-door, members-only meeting. Those who have not paid dues and have not signed a statement of non-disclosure cannot attend this meeting.

We have tentatively scheduled two of our members to present at this event.

Since it will be a long time since we had a members-only meeting, and due to the new members who have joined us, we will make this event a little more social.

We will do introductions around the room, and every member can briefly summarize what kind of help they need and for what problem.

We may also set up round tables by experience, product, or service needed.
item.name: Closed-door, members-only January meeting
